{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, the consistency between some results of the event study and the transformer demonstrates the transformer's ability to uncover meaningful relationships between entities, complementing traditional event study analyses.",
    "Conclusion and LimitationsThis paper proposed a novel sentiment correlation-based method and a Dual Transformer model to forecast the stock prices of eight companies.",
    "Some key findings of this paper are as follows.",
    "(1) The Enhancement Transformer (encoder transformer) of our proposed Dual Transformer model can help increase the correlation strength of the companies' polarity scores.",
    "(2) The proposed Dual Transformer model with sentiments of related companies as input can outperform models like Informer and LSTM."
  ]
}